  "texts": [
    "• CRC-related surgeries (ICD-10-PCS codes 0DBN8ZX, 0DBH8ZX, 0DBE8ZX, 0DBN4ZX, 0DBH4ZX, 0D9E8ZX, 0DBH7ZX, 0DBE7ZX, 0D9H3ZX, 0D9H4ZX).This approach to phenotyping screened patients was adopted from the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention PLACES project categories [33], with a few added surgical codes and the general screening code.",
    "In addition, we removed the time window consideration for certain cases.",
    "For example, colonoscopy screening is considered up to date if completed within 10 years.",
    "Keeping this standard in mind along with the limitation that our data spans a 10 year study period, we removed all temporal considerations and marked the patient as screened if they had one of the codes listed above.",
    "Patient was excluded from the subsample if they had:• Malignant neoplasm of colon (ICD-10-CM C18).• Malignant neoplasm of sigmoid colon (ICD-10-CM C18.7)."
  ],
